# BMC Issue & Fix Reviewer (fix-only)

When the user wants **fix-only** correction without Bugbot first, or says **solo arreglar**, **bmc issue fix**, or invokes agent **`bmc-issue-fix-reviewer`** directly:

## Load skill

Read and follow: `.cursor/skills/bmc-issue-fix-reviewer/SKILL.md`

## Protocol

1. Gather diff (`branch` default, or `uncommitted` / explicit files).
2. Review against `AGENTS.md` + `.cursor/rules/`.
3. **Fix** actionable findings (not readonly).
4. Run `npm run gate:local` (or lint + test) after edits in `src/` / `server/`.
5. Report table: Severity | Location | Finding | Status (fixed/remaining).

## Full pipeline (Bugbot + fix + gates)

Use **`.cursor/skills/issue-and-fix/SKILL.md`** or **`/issue-and-fix`** — not this rule.

## Agent definition

`.cursor/agents/bmc-issue-fix-reviewer.md`
